\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\frac{1}{16n^2-1}
\frac{1}{16n^2-1}=\frac{1}{(4n-1)(4n+1)}=\frac{1}{2}\left[\frac{1}{4n-1}-\frac{1}{4n+1}\right]
~\displaystyle\sum_{n=-\infty}^\infty\dfrac{x^2}{x^2-n^2}=\pi x\cdot\cot(\pi x)
x=\dfrac14
\pi x\cdot\coth(\pi x)
